title: NFL Around the League: August 5th, 2013
itunes:title: NFL Around the League: August 5th, 2013
description:
Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling break down the most underrated storylines that you should know going into the preseason. The trio also reacts to Hall of Fame weekend and gives a call to their long-lost co-worker, Dan Hanzus.
